Update site project of OBEO's Minerva

there should be ONE eclipse's hudson job for each branch ( including trunk )

there MUST be builds parameters sets up for being able to correctly promote builds.

A BUILD_TYPE parameter. type CHOICE, values N,I,S,R 

A BUILD_ALIAS parameter. type STRING

A BUILD_SIGN parameter. type BOOLEAN

Do not forget to archive artifatcs produced by the build job. something like  
xyz.update/target/xyz.update.zip,xyz.update/target/repository/**,xyz.update/target/promotion/**